  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0da7\u0da7 \u0da9\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dbb\u0dca \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 3 \u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc2\u0dd3\u0dba \u0d86\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 million dollars in humanitarian aid from Japan to this country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Taking into account the current situation in Sri Lanka, the Japanese Embassy said that the United States of America is offering 3 million dollars as emergency humanitarian aid to UNICEF and the World Food Program to provide medicines and food that will directly benefit the Sri Lankan people.",
        "The Japanese Embassy said that the reports published in some media regarding the position of the Japanese government on the current economic crisis that Sri Lanka is facing are incorrect and misleading.",
        "The Japanese Embassy stated that Japan has paid close attention to the current difficult economic situation in Sri Lanka and the resulting humanitarian situation.",
        "The Embassy stated that Japan sincerely hopes that this aid will help to overcome the difficulties faced by the people of Sri Lanka, a long-time friend of Japan.",
        "The Japanese Embassy said that it will decide on the future support in consultation with the Sri Lankan government and other development partners, focusing on the progress of the negotiations between Sri Lanka and the International Monetary Fund and the current situation in the country.",
        "The Japanese Embassy stated that Sri Lanka will continue to receive support from Japan."
      ],
